songs.title: Something
songs.lyrics:
Something in your life is on your mind
Feeling low when the sun goes down

Maybe you can tell me where your heart is
Falling down as the days go by

There's something
There's something
There's something on your mind

Something in your eyes apear so sad
Take my hand, I'm by your side

There's something
There's something
There's something on your mind

If something in your lonely life, makes you feel unsatisfied
Call me in the morning, call me in the morning

There's something
There's something
There's something on your mind
